        "data": "<h1 class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n<p>The services update for 06/13/2023 is a minor update for <strong>Backup</strong> and <strong>Web server</strong> service and a patch update for <strong>CI</strong> service.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>DXP Cloud Stack - 06/13/2023</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"width: 727px; float: left; height: 258px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 98.125px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 102.141px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 101.141px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 380.594px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 98.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 27px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>BACKUP</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.141px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 27px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.3.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.141px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 27px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.4.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 380.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 27px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/backup:5.4.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 98.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 24px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>CI</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.141px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 24px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.0.3</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.141px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 24px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.0.4</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 380.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 24px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/jenkins:2.356-jdk8-5.0.4</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 23px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Database</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.141px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 23px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.1.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.141px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 23px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.1.2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 380.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 23px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/database:5.1.2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.125px; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">Liferay</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.141px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.2.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.141px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.2.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 380.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.4-5.2.1<br>liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.3-5.2.1</p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.2.1</p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.1-5.2.1</p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.0-5.2.1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 98.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">Search</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.141px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.1.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.141px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.1.1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 380.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 48px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">li<span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">feraycloud/elast</span></span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">icse</span></span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">arch:7.17.9-5.1.1</span></span><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><span class=\"styles__name___2EY6e\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">liferaycloud/elasticsearch:6.8.23-5.1.1</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 98.125px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>WEBSERVER</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 102.141px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\">5.1.0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 101.141px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.2.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 380.594px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 26px; background-color: #f7f8f9;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>liferaycloud/nginx:1.21.6-5.2.0</strong><br><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2>Update Instructions</h2>\n<p>Note : To take advantage of the new features and fixes provided by the 5.x stack of services, you must update your entire stack to the new 5.x images.</p>\n<h2>Change Log</h2>\n<table class=\"table table-autofit table-list table-nowrap\" style=\"margin-left: 0px; margin-right: auto; height: 116px; width: 764px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 75.1406px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 59.75px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Service Version</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 99.1875px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Ticket No.</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"background-color: #f7f8f9; width: 484.922px; height: 62px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody valign=\"top\">\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 75.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Backup<br></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 59.75px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.4.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-left\" style=\"width: 99.1875px; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">\n<p>LCD-24770</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 484.922px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 10px;\">Improve Backup Restore operation to handle API failures</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 75.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>Webserver</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 59.75px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.2.0</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.1875px; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p>LCD-25776</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 484.922px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">Add capability to fine tune nginx proxy timeouts</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 75.1406px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>CI</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 59.75px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\"><strong>5.0.4</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 99.1875px; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">\n<p>LCD-27036</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 484.922px; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; height: 22px;\">Security : Fix Critical Vulnerabilities</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2> </h2>\n<p>Note : If you need to configure Nginx proxy timeouts for your application, following environment variables are introduced. </p>\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 127.286%; height: 89px;\" border=\"1\" data-mce-id=\"__mce\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 30.1908%; height: 22px;\"><strong>Name</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 7.30396%; height: 22px;\"><strong>Default</strong></td>\n<td class=\"wysiwyg-text-align-center\" style=\"width: 89.2046%; height: 22px;\"><strong>Description</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 23px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 30.1908%; height: 23px;\"><code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_GLOBAL_TIMEOUT</code></td>\n<td style=\"width: 7.30396%; height: 23px;\"><code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">60s</code></td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.2046%; height: 23px;\">\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"3641\"><em data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LEGAC</em>Y - just included for backward compatibility</p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"3692\">Sets values for the following nginx timeout configurations:</p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"3753\"><a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_connect_timeout\" href=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_connect_timeout\" data-testid=\"link-with-safety\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">proxy_connect_timeout</a> <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_read_timeout\" href=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_read_timeout\" data-testid=\"link-with-safety\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">proxy_read_timeout</a> <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_send_timeout\" href=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_send_timeout\" data-testid=\"link-with-safety\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">proxy_send_timeout</a></p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"3815\">This is a legacy variable that is only considered in case none of the other nginx timeout values are set (<code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_PROXY_CONNECT_TIMEOUT</code>, <code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_PROXY_READ_TIMEOUT</code>, <code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_PROXY_SEND_TIMEOUT</code>)</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 30.1908%; height: 22px;\"><code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_PROXY_CONNECT_TIMEOUT</code></td>\n<td style=\"width: 7.30396%; height: 22px;\"><code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">75s</code></td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.2046%; height: 22px;\">\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"4609\">Sets the nginx timeout value for connecting to haproxy / Liferay</p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"4676\">See nginx docs here: <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_connect_timeout\" href=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_connect_timeout\" data-testid=\"link-with-safety\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">proxy_connect_timeout</a></p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"4720\">If this variable is set it will override any proxy_connect_timeout values set through <code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_GLOBAL_TIMEOUT</code></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 22px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 30.1908%; height: 22px;\"><code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_PROXY_READ_TIMEOUT</code></td>\n<td style=\"width: 7.30396%; height: 22px;\"><code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">5m</code></td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.2046%; height: 22px;\">Sets the nginx timeout value for reading from haproxy / Liferay\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"4949\">See nginx docs here: <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_read_timeout\" href=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_read_timeout\" data-testid=\"link-with-safety\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">proxy_read_timeout</a></p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"4991\">If this variable is set it will override any proxy_read_timeout values set through <code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_GLOBAL_TIMEOUT</code></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30.1908%;\"><code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_PROXY_SEND_TIMEOUT</code></td>\n<td style=\"width: 7.30396%;\"><code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">5m</code></td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.2046%;\">\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"5151\">Sets the nginx timeout value for sending requests to haproxy / Liferay</p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"5224\">See nginx docs here: <a class=\"css-tgpl01\" title=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_send_timeout\" href=\"http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_proxy_module.html#proxy_send_timeout\" data-testid=\"link-with-safety\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">proxy_send_timeout</a></p>\n<p data-renderer-start-pos=\"5266\">If this variable is set it will override any proxy_send_timeout values set through <code class=\"code css-z5oxh7\" data-renderer-mark=\"true\">LCP_WEBSERVER_GLOBAL_TIMEOUT</code></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"pm-table-container \" style=\"width: inherit;\" data-layout=\"default\">\n<div class=\"pm-table-wrapper\"></div>\n</div>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h2>Image Update Instructions</h2>\n<p>The Liferay Cloud image versions needs to be set inside of the &lt;service&gt;/LCP.json file.</p>\n<p>Note, however, that the liferay service uses two image properties. The DXP Cloud image is set in the liferay/LCP.json file, but the liferay/dxp image is set in the gradle.properties. This change was made in order to facilitate easier deployment using the Liferay Cloud CLI.</p>\n<p>liferay/LCP.json file would set the liferaycloud/liferay-dxp image:</p>\n<pre><span>\"image\"</span>:<span>\"liferaycloud/liferay-dxp:7.2-5.0.X\"</span></pre>\n<p>liferay/gradle.properties file would set the liferay/dxp image:</p>\n<pre><span>liferay.workspace.docker.image.liferay</span>=<span>liferay/dxp:7.4-x</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"></span></pre>\n<p>For all other images, you will just need to update the LCP.json file with the intended image version.</p>\n<p>Once the LCP.json files are updated, commit the changes to your Git repository.</p>\n<pre>git add . &amp;&amp; git commit -m \"Update dxp cloud stack to XXX\"</pre>\n<p>After pushing these changes to the remote repository, a build will be created in Liferay Cloud and it is ready to deploy.</p>"
      },
